 class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// canvasからすべて削除</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">clearHitRegions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"clearHitRegionsメソッドを使う"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">策定状況</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#dom-context-2d-clearhitregions\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearHitRegions の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザー実装状況","id":"ブラウザー実装状況","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearHitRegions","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.addHitRegion()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/removeHitRegion\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.removeHitRegion()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"t